{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They will never again in their whole life make so much money as they could make then, in these last couple of days.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some-- obviously, some-- some Jews told them where the money is-- under which tree is it dug in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And others-- well, they rather die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I'm not going to tell them, because they told their grandchildren where it is, and they thought they will have it after the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they just put up with the suffering and luckily, most of them died the same night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were beaten up so badly, bruised everywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Anyhow, that's just a-- I don't want to go on about this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So anyhow, that's how the days went past.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And finally, it was our turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, one morning at 5 o'clock, came the Hungarian military police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And oh!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, bloody Jews!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Quick march.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they put us-- no that-- that was actually at nighttime, not in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "At nighttime, they put us in the central synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The whole-- the next day's transport, maybe 6,000 people, were jammed into the synagogue so tightly that people had to lie on the-- on the Torah and-- and every possible place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was lying between two benches, together with 10 other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "People urinated on the spot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was no-- no toilets or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, we were young boys, so I mean, we could take anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I mean, there were old people there, grandmothers, and babies, and newly-born babies, and sick people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The dead bodies had to-- were thrown into the rabbi's office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a rabbi's office, where it was chockablock full with dead bodies, already piled up high-- nobody to bury them or take them away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyhow, luckily next morning then they opened the doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
